    "intended": "Let $f(z)=\\prod_{i=1}^n(z-z_i)\\in \\mathbb{C}[z]$ with $\\lvert z_i\\rvert \\leq 1$ for all $i$. Let $\\rho(f)$ be the radius of the largest disc which is contained in $\\{z: \\lvert f(z)\\rvert< 1\\}$. \n\nDetermine the behaviour of $\\rho(f)$. In particular, is it always true that $\\rho(f)\\gg 1/n$?",
